# Expense Insurance Total Ultimate Cost Net Reinsurance And Non Reinsurance Recoveries Amount

## identifier
de8561

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of the total net ultimate cost (inflated & undiscounted) of claims, as at the relevant date.

This item represents the sum of:
     - net claims payment expenses incurred, as at the relevant date;
     - net case estimates, as at the relevant date; and
     - net claims incurred but not reported (IBNR)/incurred but not enough reported (IBNER), as at the relevant date;

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Expense.Insurance.TotalUltimateCostNetReinsuranceAndNonReinsuranceRecoveries.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr3.02.05
- period=instant
